title: Ygritt's detonating sphere
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

When this small silver sphere is thrown, it detonates on impact and deals acid damage and arcane force damage to all creatures within a 10-foot radius. The sphere can be retrieved and reused if it is boiled in water for 8 hours.